      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Medical)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 5</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>As Iryou Ninjutsu: Chiyu - Shodan Jutsu. The healing is increased to 1d6+2 HP per minute. Discharging the technique can be done only by a character with Medical Specialist level 4 or higher, and heals 3d6 HP, +1 per level (maximum +10).</p>\n\n\n\n",
